<div class="demo">
  <h1>Example heading <span class="目標">New</span></h1> 
</div>


<h2>標準範例</h2>

<p>他自動符合各種尺寸</p>

<div class="demo">
  <h5>Example heading <span class="badge badge-secondary">New</span></h5>
  <h6>Example heading <span class="badge badge-secondary">New</span></h6>
</div>


<p>可以作為連結或按鈕的計數器</p>

<div class="demo">
  <button class="btn btn-primary">
    Notifications <span class="badge badge-light">4</span>
  </button>
</div>


<h2>情境變化</h2>

<p>加入以下的色彩 Class 來修改標籤的外觀 (primary, secondary, success, danger, warning, info, light, dark)。</p>

<div class="demo">
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Primary</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Secondary</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Success</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Danger</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Warning</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Info</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Light</span>
  <span class="badge badge-目標">Dark</span>
</div>


<h2>膠囊標籤</h2>

<p>使用 .badge-pill 可以使標籤更圓潤</p>

<div class="demo">
  <span class="badge 目標 badge-primary">Primary</span>
  <span class="badge 目標 badge-secondary">Secondary</span>
  <span class="badge 目標 badge-success">Success</span>
  <span class="badge 目標 badge-danger">Danger</span>
</div>


<h2>連結</h2>

<p>將以下 span 改為 a 元素並加上 href="#"，提供 hover 和 focus 狀態</p>

<div class="demo">
  <span class="badge badge-primary">Primary</span>
  <span class="badge badge-secondary">Secondary</span>
  <span class="badge badge-success">Success</span>
</div>
